reviews.text: Today here on 3 May 2025 delicious lunch and some incredibly friendly spontaneous staff , nice tent on a cozy part in Borne

reviews.title: Great food, pleasant staff
reviews.text: The service was fine, maybe ask a little less often if it tastes. We had bread with herb butter beforehand, this was a bit small sandwich for the price 4.75. The main courses were tasty, pork tenderloin could have been a little less far. The fries were very tasty, the baked potatoes were a bit soft and tasteless.

reviews.title: Top food and good friendly service.
reviews.text: Neat and fast service, I had a special wish that could be fulfilled. 100 points for the alley.

reviews.title: Perfect schnitzel
reviews.text: Authentic Pub in the Borne city with nice outdoor seating, friendly service and a perfect schnitzel De Steeg with mushrooms, bacon nicely fried fries and a fresh site salad.

reviews.title: Spareribs and Ribeye
reviews.text: Fantastic kitchen. Great cook. Dinner is cooked almost to perfection. Service is great. Would really recommend a visit to this cozy pub-restaurant.

reviews.title: Great pub food
reviews.text: Our visit to this place was a great pleasure. Good food and friendly staff. Good value for money. You can sit insiders the typical Dutch brown pub, or outside.

reviews.title: Nice environment, good food
reviews.text: Nice place, relaxed atmosphere, good food, decent price. Menu is not very extensive, but there are enough options on the menu to find something for everyone.
